    <h1 itemprop="headline" class=" ">George W Bush&#039;s ethics lawyer says Jeff Sessions&#039; denial of Russia talks &#039;a good way to go to jail&#039;</h1>

    
            <div class="intro">
                <p>Justice Department maintains 'there was absolutely nothing misleading about his answer'</p>
      </div>
            <ul class="caption meta inline-pipes-list">
              <li class="author" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
          <span itemprop="name"><a href="/author/jon-sharman" title="Jon Sharman" itemprop="sameAs">Jon Sharman</a></span>
                  </li>
                          <li title="2 March 2017 14:03 London"><time data-microtimes='{"published":"1488463380000","display":0,"changed":"1488463380000"}' datetime="Thu, 03/02/2017 - 14:03">Thursday 2 March 2017 14:03 GMT</time></li>
